---
const WHATSAPP_LINK = "https://wa.me/77055606066";
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="py-20 px-4 border-t border-white/5 bg-dark-bg">
  <div class="container mx-auto">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-12 mb-16">
      <div class="lg:col-span-2">
        <div class="text-2xl font-black mb-6 text-white uppercase tracking-wider">Astro<span class="text-neon-cyan">Studio</span></div>
        <p class="text-white/50 max-w-sm mb-8">
          Мы создаем будущее веба для вашего бизнеса. Быстро, стильно и на века.
        </p>
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <a href={WHATSAPP_LINK} target="_blank" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full glass flex items-center justify-center hover:border-neon-cyan transition-colors">
            <span class="text-neon-cyan">WA</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div>
        <h4 class="text-lg font-bold mb-6">Контакты</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-4 text-white/50">
          <li><a href="tel:+77055606066" class="hover:text-neon-cyan transition-colors">+7 (705) 560-60-66</a></li>
          <li>Kazakhstan, Digital Nomad</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <div>
        <h4 class="text-lg font-bold mb-6">Действие</h4>
        <a 
          href={WHATSAPP_LINK}
          target="_blank"
          class="inline-block glass px-6 py-3 rounded-xl text-neon-cyan border-neon-cyan/20 hover:bg-neon-cyan/10 transition-all font-bold"
        >
          Начать проект
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center pt-8 border-t border-white/5 text-white/30 text-sm">
      <p>&copy; {currentYear} AstroStudio. Все права защищены.</p>
      <p class="mt-4 md:mt-0">Сделано с ❤️ на Astro</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
